data.description: Great home in popular Raintree Place in Brandon! Convenient location, large corner lot & efficient floor plan combine to make this home a winner! Inside you will find real wood floors, a living room with fresh paint, fireplace & a cased opening into the dining room.  The bright & cheery kitchen has new countertops, a pantry and an easy- to-access laundry area.  Primary bedroom also has fresh paint and a walk-in closet, plus a large bath w/double sinks. 2 guest bedrooms (one with tall ceilings) and a guest bath complete the tour. Don't miss out on the chance to own  this attractive home in the heart of Brandon and only minutes away from many dining and shopping options!
